sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Client
  participant Wallet as Wallet (Pera)
  participant Router as Router (:3001)
  participant Algorand as Algorand (TestNet)

  Note over Client,Algorand: Phase A - agent onboards into the IdentityRegistry
  Client->>Wallet: register agent (agentURI, metadata)
  Wallet->>Algorand: signed register() txn
  Algorand-->>Wallet: agentId minted (owner = agentWallet = sender)
  Note right of Algorand: canonical id = {agentRegistry, agentId}
  Wallet-->>Client: registered (txid to explorer)
  Note over Router: boot seedProviders() writes agents into ctx.providers
  Note over Router: chain to router adapter is a seam, not wired yet

  Note over Client,Algorand: Phase B - client request routed to that agent
  Client->>Router: POST /api/route {task, register}
  Note right of Router: discover(ctx.providers) filter by register tag
  Note right of Router: price from provider.quote, rank (repState reroute on re-run)
  Router-->>Client: route_id + ranked options[] (option_id maps to provider_id)

  Client->>Router: POST /api/pay {route_id, option_id}
  Note right of Router: resolve option.provider_id to provider.register (payTo)
  Router->>Algorand: settle() real ALGO to provider
  Algorand-->>Router: txid + confirmed round
  Router->>Algorand: anchorNote() 0-ALGO hash-only ledger txn
  Algorand-->>Router: anchor txid + round
  Router-->>Client: payment_id, txids, quoted, settled

  opt operator signs the settlement self-anchor
    Client->>Wallet: Sign on TestNet
    Wallet->>Algorand: signed 0-ALGO self-anchor (x402.settle.pera)
    Algorand-->>Wallet: txid to ledger
  end

  Note over Client,Algorand: Feedback loop - changes future routing
  Client->>Router: POST /api/validate {payment_id}
  Note right of Router: price_match (settled <= quoted), response 0|60|100
  Note right of Router: repState.writeBack(provider_id) reroutes on re-run
  Router->>Algorand: anchorNote() verdict hash
  Algorand-->>Router: verdict_txid
  Router-->>Client: price_match, response, new_reputation, verdict_txid
